elements.name: User should able create an account and create a workout

steps.name: Launch any browser and navigate to site
Select Create Account option
Enter details and click on sign up button to create new Tacx account
Verify the URL in App dashboard
Select “Create workout” menu item from left pane in dashboard
Select Power workout and then select distance as target and then select continue
Set distance to 12 KM and save the workout with title name "New Workout - 12 km"
navigate to “Workouts” menu item and verify the created new Workout with mentioned title name
Logout from Account

elements.name: User should  with same credentials and double click on arrows

steps.name: Launch any browser and navigate to site
User enter the same credentials
Verify the URL in App dashboard
Select “Create workout” menu item from left pane in dashboard
Select Power workout and then select distance as target and then select continue
User right click on the arrow up button
Set distance to 12 KM and save the workout with title name "New Workout - 12 km"
navigate to “Workouts” menu item and verify the created new Workout with mentioned title name
Logout from Account

elements.name: User should not able to create an account with invalid name

Select Create Account option
Enter invalid name and others and click on sign up button to create new Tacx account
